edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.design
Class PIP

java.lang.Object
  edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.design.PIP
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<java.lang.Object>
public class PIP
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<java.lang.Object>, java.io.Serializable

This class represents the programmable-interconnect-points (PIPs) as found in XDL designs. The wire names are stored as integers using the WireEnumerator found in the edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.device class.

Author:
Chris Lavin Created on: Jun 22, 2010
